text: Gustave Fahy (1 March 1880 - 18 August 1967) was a French gymnast. He competed in the men's individual all-around event at the 1900 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1880 births Category:1967 deaths Category:French male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of France Category:Gymnasts at the 1900 Summer Olympics Category:People from Nanterre
